<p>
  <span class="nym">Guardia</span>
  <span class="gen">f.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Italian</span> <i>guardia</i>, from <span class="lang">Latin</span> <i>gardia</i> 'wardship, guardianship', <span class="lang">Spanish</span> <i>guarda</i> 'guard, ward'.
</span>
  
</p>
  
  


